#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/flags.rst:23
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_OBJ_FLAG_SCROLL_ONE`: Allow scrolling only one "
"snappable child."
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_OBJ_FLAG_SCROLL_ONE`: Consente lo scrolling di un solo elemento figlio \"snappable\" [agganciabile]."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/flags.rst:24
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_OBJ_FLAG_SCROLL_CHAIN_HOR`: Propagate horizontal "
