msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_OBJ_FLAG_SCROLL_CHAIN_HOR`: Propaga lo scorrimento orizzontale all'elemento padre."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/flags.rst:25
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_OBJ_FLAG_SCROLL_CHAIN_VER`: Propagate vertical "
"scrolling to the parent."
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_OBJ_FLAG_SCROLL_CHAIN_VER`: Propaga lo scorrimento verticale all'elemento padre."

