msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_OBJ_FLAG_SCROLL_CHAIN`: Shorthand for "
"`SCROLL_CHAIN_HOR | SCROLL_CHAIN_VER`."
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_OBJ_FLAG_SCROLL_CHAIN`: Abbreviazione di `SCROLL_CHAIN_HOR | SCROLL_CHAIN_VER`."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/flags.rst:27
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_OBJ_FLAG_SCROLL_ON_FOCUS`: Automatically scroll to "
