":cpp:enumerator:`LV_OBJ_FLAG_SNAPPABLE`: Allow the widget to be snapped "
"if the parent has scroll snapping enabled."
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_OBJ_FLAG_SNAPPABLE`: Consente lo \"snap\" [aggancio] del widget se l'elemento padre ha abilitato l'aggancio con scorrimento."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/flags.rst:30
