"horizontal and top when vertical. (default)"
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_GRID_ALIGN_START`: indica sinistra quando la direzione è orizzontale e in alto quando è verticale. (Il default)."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/layouts/grid.rst:107
msgid ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_GRID_ALIGN_CENTER`: simply center"
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_GRID_ALIGN_CENTER`: semplicemente centra"

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/layouts/grid.rst:108
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_GRID_ALIGN_SPACE_EVENLY`: items are distributed so "
"that the spacing between any two items (and the space to the edges) is "
"equal. Not applies to ``track_cross_place``."
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_GRID_ALIGN_SPACE_EVENLY`: gli elementi sono distribuiti in modo che la spaziatura tra due elementi qualsiasi (e lo spazio fino ai bordi) sia uguale. Non si applica a ``track_cross_place``."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/layouts/grid.rst:110
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_GRID_ALIGN_SPACE_AROUND`: items are evenly "
"distributed in the track with equal space around them. Note that visually"
" the spaces aren't equal, since all the items have equal space on both "
"sides. This makes the space between items double the space between edge "
"items and the container's edge. Does not apply to ``track_cross_place``."
