#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/layouts/grid.rst:115
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_GRID_ALIGN_SPACE_BETWEEN`: items are evenly "
"distributed in the track with first and last items next to container's "
"edges. Does not apply to ``track_cross_place``."
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_GRID_ALIGN_SPACE_BETWEEN`: gli elementi sono distribuiti uniformemente nella track con il primo e l'ultimo elemento adiacenti ai bordi del contenitore. Non si applica a ``track_cross_place``."

