#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/screens.rst:88
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_MOVE_LEFT`, "
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_MOVE_RIGHT`, "
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_MOVE_TOP` and "
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_MOVE_BOTTOM`: Move both the current "
"and new screens towards the given direction"
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_MOVE_LEFT`, :cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_MOVE_RIGHT`, :cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_MOVE_TOP` e :cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_MOVE_BOTTOM`: Spostano sia lo Screen corrente che quello nuovo nella direzione indicata"

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/screens.rst:93
msgid ""
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_FADE_IN` and "
":cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_FADE_OUT`: Fade the new screen over "
"the old screen, or vice versa"
msgstr ":cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_FADE_IN` e :cpp:enumerator:`LV_SCREEN_LOAD_ANIM_FADE_OUT`: Dissolvenza del nuovo Screen su quello precedente, o viceversa."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/screens.rst:97
msgid ""
"The new Screen will become active (returned by "
":cpp:func:`lv_screen_active`) when the animation starts after ``delay`` "
"time."
msgstr "Il nuovo Screen diventerà attivo (restituito da :cpp:func:`lv_screen_active`) quando l'animazione inizia dopo il tempo ``delay``."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/common-widget-features/screens.rst:100
msgid ""
"All input device events (e.g. touch, keys, etc) are disabled during the "
"Screen's animation."
msgstr "Tutti gli eventi dei dispositivi di input (ad esempio touch, tasti, ecc.) sono disabilitati durante l'animazione dello Screen."

